SP.P:
This now is like a Husbands love; free as it should be;

Which mine shall qual, and now I'll boldly say,

Whensoe'er yours was, this is my Wedding day.

The Devil's in't, that this should happen thus. Aside. Well, Sir, though this be an odd turn in fortune, yet never shall any breach of promise taint my Honor;

Here take her, She's yours, and now he hold to say▪

Midst all Ill-Luck, This is your happy day.
